'''Sith spy''' was a [[Military rank/Legends|rank]] during the [[New Sith Wars]]. The [[Brotherhood of Darkness/Legends|Brotherhood of Darkness]] [[Sith training|trained]] them in the [[Sith Academy (Ryloth)|Ryloth Academy]], [[Sith Academy (Umbara)|Umbara Academy]], and [[Sith Academy (Nar Shaddaa)|Nar Shaddaa Academy]]. [[Umbaran/Legends|Umbaran]] [[Umbaran Shadow Assassin|shadow spies]] were one type of [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] [[Spy/Legends|spy]].

